column2: I am disgusted that the ACLU colluded with Amber Heard to create a false op-ed to destroy an innocent man. I will never trust this organization again. And how dare they now charge Mr. Depp for the time they spent gathering their self-damning documentation, after repeatedly refusing to co-operate with a court order to turn over the evidence.

column52: The ACLU conspired with Amber Heard to ruin Johnny Depp with the article they helped Amber Heard author and publish in the Washington Post.
